about.summary: Provides visualizations for 'mlr3' objects such as tasks, predictions, resample results or benchmark results via the autoplot() generic of 'ggplot2'. The returned 'ggplot' objects are intended to provide sensible defaults, yet can easily be customized to create camera-ready figures. Visualizations include barplots, boxplots, histograms, ROC curves, and Precision-Recall curves.

name: r-mlr3viz
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.5.0' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-mlr3viz
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/mlr3viz_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/mlr3viz/mlr3viz_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b49a5d8413eb73d6a8895d19e2baa1da1623c9d92b9b2a76dfa3650e26fed897

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-checkmate
    - r-data.table
    - r-ggplot2 >=3.3.0
    - r-mlr3misc
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-checkmate
    - r-data.table
    - r-ggplot2 >=3.3.0
    - r-mlr3misc

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('mlr3viz')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('mlr3viz')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://mlr3viz.mlr-org.com, https://github.com/mlr-org/mlr3viz
  license: LGPL-3.0-only
  summary: Provides visualizations for 'mlr3' objects such as tasks, predictions, resample results
    or benchmark results via the autoplot() generic of 'ggplot2'. The returned 'ggplot'
    objects are intended to provide sensible defaults, yet can easily be customized
    to create camera-ready figures. Visualizations include barplots, boxplots, histograms,
    ROC curves, and Precision-Recall curves.
  license_family: LGPL
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/LGPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - pascal-git
